<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3718.1.2>
    dc:creator "Abo-Shnaf, Reham I. A.; Castilho, Raphael C.; De Moraes, Gilberto J." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Rhodacaridae (Acari: Mesostigmata) from Egypt and a key to the species of the family from the Mediterranean region" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222301>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222302> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222301>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Multidentorhodacarus aegypticus n. sp. Female. 1. Chelicera; 2. Epistome; 3. Hypostome; 4. Dorsal idiosoma; 5. Ventral idiosoma; 6. Tritosternum. Lyrifissures enlarged for better visibility." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222302>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 9. Multidentorhodacarus aegypticus n. sp. Male. 7. Chelicera, showing two of the observed spermatodactyl orientations; 8. Ventral idiosoma; 9. Dorsal view of femur, genu and tibia of right leg II. Lyrifissures enlarged for better visibility." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

